You have successfully disconnected your Facebook account from our store account.,"Uspešno ste odjavili Facebook račun z naše trgovine."

Lahko se prijavite z uporabo Facebook prijavnega gumba ali poverilnic naše trgovine prejetih po eletronski pošti."

Since Twitter doesn\'t support third-party access to your email address, we were unable to send you your store accout credentials. To be able to login using store account credentials you will need to update your email address and password using our Edit Account Information.","Ker Twitter ne podpira dostopa zunanjih aplikacij do vašega e-poštnega naslova, vam ne moremo polati poverilnic vašega računa. Za uporabo računa trgovine morate posodobiti e-poštni naslov in geslo z uporabo Posodobi informacije računa."
